            <fr:title text="Baby steps in higher domain theory › is the partial map classifier a Sierpiński cone? (V)"><fr:link href="jms-00RN.xml" title="Baby steps in higher domain theory" addr="jms-00RN" type="local">Baby steps in higher domain theory</fr:link> › is the partial map classifier a Sierpiński cone? (V)</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Slide</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>In the case of dcpos, unique extensions of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  \bot {\mathopen {}\left (A\right )\mathclose {}}\to  C]]></fr:tex> along the comparison map <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\bot {\mathopen {}\left (A\right )\mathclose {}}\to  L{\mathopen {}\left (A\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> are obtained by taking the <fr:em>colimits</fr:em> of diagrams <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\bot {\mathopen {}\left (i=1\right )\mathclose {}}\to  C]]></fr:tex>:</fr:p>
            <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[
  \begin {aligned}
   L{\mathopen {}\left (A\right )\mathclose {}} &\to  C \\
   {\mathopen {}\left \langle i,a\right \rangle \mathclose {}} &\mapsto 
   \operatorname {colim}_{\bot {\mathopen {}\left (i=1\right )\mathclose {}}}
   {\mathopen {}\left  [f{\mathopen {}\left (\bot \right )\mathclose {}} \mid  p:i=1\hookrightarrow  f{\mathopen {}\left (\eta {\mathopen {}\left (a{\mathopen {}\left (p\right )\mathclose {}}\right )\mathclose {}}\right )\mathclose {}}\right  ]\mathclose {}}
  \end {aligned}
 ]]></fr:tex>
            <beamer:pause xmlns:beamer="http://ctan.org/pkg/beamer" />
            <fr:p>Perhaps we can use the same idea.</fr:p>
            <beamer:pause xmlns:beamer="http://ctan.org/pkg/beamer" />
            <fr:p><fr:strong>Conjecture.</fr:strong> The comparison map <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\bot {\mathopen {}\left (A\right )\mathclose {}}\to  L{\mathopen {}\left (A\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> is left orthogonal to any Rezk type closed under colimits of shape <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\bot {\mathopen {}\left (i=1\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> in the sense of <fr:link href="bardomiano-mart%C3%ADnez-2023.xml" title="Limits and exponentiable functors in simplicial homotopy type theory" addr="bardomiano-martínez-2023" type="local">Bardomiano Martínez</fr:link>.</fr:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
